  <num>37-201.08</num>
  <heading>Commodities sold by weight; "ton" defined.</heading>
  <formerly-cited-as>DC ST 1981 § 10-109</formerly-cited-as>
  <text>When any commodity is sold by weight it shall be net weight. When any commodity is sold by the ton, it shall be understood to mean 2,000 pounds avoirdupois.</text>
